<br />
A1, S2: Duke Ellington; John Coltrane; Dizzy Gillespie; Cole Porter; Shearing-Foster, Charlie Parker<br />
<br />
A2, S1:<br />
G. &amp; I. Gershwin; Art Tatum (arranged); Dizzy Gillespie; Jose Ferrer; Thelonious Monk; Adriano Acea<br />
<br />
A2, S2: <br />
William York; Green-Wolf; Lester Young, Basie-Rushing; Eckstine-Hines; Dietz-Schwartz</div>
